{"tid":1537062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議］全城光復母校 點醒師弟師妹","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:46:59.000Z","uid":246637,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1457857fa02ddfa36fe768283537dae98b7ac48","tid":1537062,"uid":246637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:46:22.000Z","msg":"眼見中學生罷課唔算好高參與，因為聽返啲中學生講其實知道佢哋好多都唔了解呢幾個月發生緊咩事，加上好多學校同老師都唔支持罷課。<br />\n<br />\n正如大陸人覺得大陸無自由無問題一樣，下一代喺有問題嘅環境中成長，即使長大都會因為習慣而唔察覺有問題。<br />\n所以我哋必須及早開導下一代嘅思想！發起一場光復母校嘅運動！由大家一齊返到母校，幫師弟妹覺醒。<br />\n<br />\n我哋最大目標<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>唔係要中學生罷課、上街示威、或者一定要抱有咩政治立場</strong></span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>目標篇：</strong></span><br />\n1. 令中學生了解清楚香港政治狀況及政策問題<br />\n2. 令中學生了解五大訴求<br />\n3. 呼籲中學生登記/準備登記選民<br />\n4. 批評會秋後算帳罷課學生的學校<br />\n5. 呼籲中學生分享見聞予親友</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>籌辦篇：</strong></span></span><br />\n1. 舊生可以利用平時學校<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>secret gp</strong></span>籌辦<br />\n2. 自發一班師兄師姐，一齊探訪母校<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>（最好用telegram溝通，以便匿名）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>執行篇：</strong></span></span><br />\n1.印刷大量<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>文宣派發</strong></span> e.g.於學校門口派發/攝入locker等。<br />\n2. 如校方許可，於校內設<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>連儂牆</strong></span>；如校方不許可則建議學生到附近連儂場觀察<br />\n3. 趁學生放學/放飯<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>說教</strong></span><br />\n4. 建議學生<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>聯署簽名</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>物資篇：</strong></span></span><br />\n1. 印刷大量富有<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">教育性、資訊性的文宣</span></strong><br />\nE.g. 逃犯條例的影響、黑警濫權、雙普選的重要性、自由的重要性......<br />\n2. 提供<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>口罩、紗布、絲帶</strong></span>予適用之罷課學生<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: green;\">Memo紙、膠紙、剪刀</span></strong><br />\n4.充足<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>人手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>提醒篇：</strong></span></span><br />\n1. 唔建議喺學校高呼口號，免得惹起投訴及衝突<br />\n2. 不要強行塗污及損壞學校設施<br />\n3. 任何於校內進行的行動，必須先經校方同意；否則進行於校門外</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">歡迎大家作補充及改善此方案</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"4f23679e34016843aeab97900e769f430c4b4056","tid":1537062,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:47:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBWrQR5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiBWrQR5.jpg&h=8316617f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"637cf0734ce3f43f30f37c00df37673a3e4fc8e8","tid":1537062,"uid":297850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LVPMQ5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLVPMQ5s.jpg&h=a695cad4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e53cd6485f14bac3504025d583676f8df7a9b9ea","tid":1537062,"uid":246637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:55:48.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhhhhh"},{"pid":"5bea8b42f72018c46a7976543fd558eac81e6d48","tid":1537062,"uid":246637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:56:23.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhhh"},{"pid":"bd33ffd888d60256477c1c0861d450490cd45b54","tid":1537062,"uid":246637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:56:33.000Z","msg":"Pppppppush"},{"pid":